high_descs: Go around the sofa and the arm chair and get to the other side of the coffee table.
Pick up the remote on the table.
Turn right and go to the arm chair and the foot rest.
Place the remote between the phone and the newspaper.
Turn around and go around the table and the sofa to face the left side of the sofa.
Pick up the remote on the sofa seat.
Go around the coffee table back to the arm chair.
Place the remote on the foot rest behind the phone next to the first remote.
anns.task_desc: Put both remotes on the foot rest.

high_descs: move to the coffee table in front of the fire place
pick up a remote from the table
move to the ottoman in front arm chair to the right of the coffee table
put the remote on the ottoman
move to the couch in front of the fire place
pick up a remote from the couch
move to the ottoman in front arm chair to the right of the coffee table
put the remote on the ottoman
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on a ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the chair, take a left around the coffee table and hang a right at the wall to face the coffee table on the right.
Pick up the silver remote in between the two laptop computers.
Turn to the right to face the ottoman of the chair.
Place the remote near the edge of the ottoman between the cell phone and the newspaper.
Turn around, hang a right at the fireplace, hang a left at the couch, turn right at the black side table and face the arm of the couch to the right.
Pick up the silver remote near the book on the couch cushion.
Turn right, hang a left at the fireplace and walk to the ottoman of the chair.
Put the remote on the left side of the ottoman above the red cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Place two remote controls on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the far end of the coffee table
Pick up the remote on the coffee table
Turn to the right
set the remote down between the newspaper and the phone closest to you on the foot stool
Turn around and walk past the fireplace, turn right and go to the left side of the couch with the red jacket on it.
Pick up the remote that's on the couch
go back to the foot stool
set the remote down on the foot stool
anns.task_desc: Put both the remotes on the foot stool

high_descs: Turn around and move over to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control from the coffee table.
Bring the remote control to the purple ottoman.
Put the remote down on the ottoman.
Move over to the other side of the couch.
Pick up the remote control on the couch.
Bring that remote over to the purple ottoman.
Put that remote down on the ottoman next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn around and walk until you hit a purple chair and then maneuver yourself so you are between the coffee table and the wall looking at the sofa.
Pick up the remote control near the edge of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk forward slightly until your are near the ottoman and facing it.
Put the remote between the red phone and the newspaper sitting to the right of the red phone.
Turn around and walk until you are between the couch and a small table with a plant and face the couch so you are looking down the length of it.
Pick up the remote you see sitting on the couch by a book.
Walk back over to the ottoman and take the same position you did before.
Set the remote down above the red phone near the bottom of the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on top of the ottoman in the living room.
